print ("This is your character. His name is clover. On a fateful day clover decided to outside and touch grass. He hasn't touched grass since the heian era. As Colver touches grass he suddenly remembers how he has no food or milk. Thus clover began his quest to the local Shop rite. As clover was walking a person popped out of the bush next to him. Even with clover's attempts to not fight this guy, this guy kept pushing. Eventually Clover had to fight back and with a strike he knocks off the person's hood, revealing their character. In this adventuer you have a certain chance to encounter different enemies on your quest to find milk and food. Your chances are pretty good for someone named clover. You have a 40% chance to fight yukuna, 30% chance to fight mekuna,15% chance to fight heian sukuna, 14% chance to fight freiza. There are still 3 characters left to share the 1 percent. In the case that you encounter any of those 3 consider your run over. The 3 are jeff, the earth, 0.4 percent to spawn. Stewart, the heavens, 0.4 percent to spawn. Bob, the void,, 0.2 percent chance to spawn")